          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十八扯》一戏，虽是拉杂演唱，然亦颇不寻常。盖生旦净丑，各种唱调皆全，故向来脍炙人口，每受社会"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "欢迎。然各家脚本，初无一定，因此戏本之自由唱奏，故名角多随意增删。此《新四十八扯》，系最近北京"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某艺员新编之本，所收各剧，皆以前人缺憾事翻案，故甚有兴趣，能使人耳目一新。洵非胸无点墨者，所能"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杂凑而成也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《戏考》第三十二册整理"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄狗一去三千年，白狗乘云飞上天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赵晃，妹子赵瑶颜。这两天刚刚是新年头上，任莫都玩够了。要是嫖，破钞，\n要是赌，输钱。大长日子，没有事儿可做，倒不如把妹子叫出来，跟她商议，\n或有甚么新鲜法子来，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃向内唤。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听哥哥唤，急忙到面前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹子，今天没有什么事，你跟我想个新鲜法子，咱们解闷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放爆仗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扎花灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这不好，那不好，我就没有新鲜法子了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃捂首想。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵晃 （曰） 有了，咱们唱戏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唱什么戏？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先唱杨贵妃马嵬还魂，再唱张丽华井底逃生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么我去扮起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下。赵晃换衣扮唐明皇上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐对花名，怎禁得风雨天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朕开元天子。只为安禄山造反，杀进长安，因此带了太真妃子，翠华西幸来到\n马嵬坡下。六军不服，要将妃子生生赐死。幸亏陈元礼多方弹压，始无意外之\n虑。看看晓行夜宿，已是蜀栈，天降大雨，只得暂扎行营。对此急鼓疏命，残\n香烬烛，好生愁闷人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜扮杨贵妃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绿珠抱琴至，文君送酒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜相见行礼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾知陛下心中愁闷，备有樽酒，与陛下赏雨解闷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妃子生受你了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜作斟酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想此时御园中无穷秋景，\n抛撇了好风光来作征人。\n因此上安禄山扰动烟尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内作铃响。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "耳边厢似诉我李行艰辛。\n要比那霓裳曲花样翻新。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜吹笛唱曲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "唱一声浑不减莺啼燕鸣，\n怕只怕更漏深缟袂生冷。\n待他时返长安付与梨园。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃、赵瑶颜同下。赵瑶颜扮陈叔宝跌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤家陈叔宝，在降春园作一阙月词，不曾填罢，韩擒虎过江来了，这便如何是\n好？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃扮张丽急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔贵嫔哪里去了，为何只见爱卿一人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已被乱军杀了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜作晕。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我主醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听他言不由得我肝肠寸断，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "看襟前血和泪红似啼鹃。\n回头来寻不见文武宫员。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内喊声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "韩擒虎将到面前，我与爱卿须要寻一地方藏躲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜指。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胭脂井！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜、赵晃同作跳入下。赵晃扮韩擒虎、赵瑶颜扮兵卒同绕场下。赵瑶颜扮陈叔宝、赵晃扮张丽华同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好了好了，韩擒虎人马过去了，我二人不免乔装改扮，往别处逃生去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旧恨新愁未有涯，萍飘梗泛已无家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红心三月官人草，碧血千年帝子花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜、赵晃同下。赵晃僧装挑担扮建文帝上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "山河大地今何有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今古兴亡貉一邱。\n一瓢一笠学云游。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃放担坐。赵瑶颜扮程济上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师在哪里？大师在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "程济为何这等慌张？敢是燕番的追兵来了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并不是燕番追兵来了，刚才到附近村庄抄花斋粮，听得他们纷纷言讲：各路勤\n王兵到，把燕藩杀了，连那道衍也做了刀头之鬼，现在要找寻大师回去重为九\n五之尊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当真？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可想见世间事白衣苍狗，\n谢只谢各路里忠义貔貅。\n到如今只落得万事全休。\n想起了先帝爷两泪交流。\n紫金山莽苍苍又是残秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃、赵瑶颜同下。内吹打。赵晃白须戎装扮史可法上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "法摇山岳动，令出鬼神惊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本阁部史可法。奉了福王之命，镇守扬州。幸我帐下大小儿郎，同心协力，将\n北兵杀得上天无路，入地无门。北王情愿讲和，永远不侵疆界，真是好生侥幸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "先帝爷在煤山龙归海境，\n有老臣保幼主重整朝廷。\n只杀得众儿郎动魄惊心。\n写降书和降表永不相侵。\n白发人还能够歌舞太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜扮天使持圣旨上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨下，跪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉天承运，圣帝诏曰：尔史可法，一战成功。北营中情愿年年进贡，岁岁来朝，\n朕心深为喜悦，今封史可法为定北王之职，钦此。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃叩头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁万岁！\n吩咐后营备酒，与天使接风。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝命在身，不敢久恋，就此告辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下。赵晃送，换衣。〖吹打〗。赵晃下。赵晃挂黑须上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三尺黄泉万卷书，彼苍生我意如何。山东出将山西相，彼丈夫乎我丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下官林则徐。因焚弃洋烟触了外人之忌，圣上将我官阶革去，发往新疆，效力\n在半路上，忽蒙恩旨钦召回京，看看已是黄河。\n家院！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "预备船只伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "莽苍苍又来到九曲黄河，\n拍长空好比那雪练横拖。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃作登船。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "在船中一霎时摇摇欲坠，\n敌不过宦海中险恶风波。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃下。赵瑶颜扮武小生田兴恕上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "九龙宿帐春无草，万马窥边夜有霜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅田兴恕。幼年投管效力，立下汗马功劳，官拜提督之职。为着一时鲁莽，\n杀了本省藩司，圣上将我发充烟瘴。行到半途呈上，因捻匪十分猖獗，左爵帅\n将我截留在营，命我戴罪立功，好不兴头人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "红巾贼受天诛四方无事，\n又出了小妖魔占夺城池。\n左爵帅统貔貅昼夜奔驰。\n只杀得沙场上血染胭脂。\n少不得金鸡诏飞下丹墀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下。赵晃扮差官上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱家，长江水师提督辕门上差官是也。我家大人夺回小姑山之后，十分喜悦，\n命我在船中预备酒筵伺候，远远看见大人来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜扮芒鞋竹杖挂白须上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "看长江无波浪澄清如镜，\n对着那小姑山一点摇青。\n怕只怕有蛟龙水底潜听。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃扮作换。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵晃 （吴歌） 奔涛东去响如雷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阵马风船付劫灰。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "彭郎夺得小姑回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈妙吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一霎时又只见天升玉镜，\n挽雕弓射落了斗大妖星。\n伴闲人可有个鼓瑟湘灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下，扮船婆上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赵瑶颜 （吴歌） 莫愁湖上荡轻舟，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "日见鸳鸯总并头。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁家少妇在红楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，秦淮河里船婆。曾大帅克复南京，要我们来兴市面，有些王孙公子叫我把\n他摇来摇去，尽情作乐。有时还赏我大把的银钱。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一盏寒泉荐秋菊，三更画船穿藕花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃方巾便服挂桥白须上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这几日看不尽画兰桡桨，\n一个个卖风流红粉娇娘。\n又只见夜朦胧一片灯光。\n回头来又想起发逆猖狂。\n每夜里枕戈眠不到甜乡。\n也不枉顾命臣整顿一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃下。赵瑶颜戎装上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七十二载，战无不利。忽闻楚歌，一败涂地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤家拿破仑。自为英将惠林吞所败，各国国王公议，将我放在爱来巴岛，宫花\n寂寞，海水苍凉，叫孤家如何消受？是我设下一计，将岛官灌醉，逃回故国，\n重带精兵三十万，要与惠林吞看见个高低。来此已是滑铁卢了，吩咐将营扎下。\n正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "令严鼓角三更月，户纳貔貅万灶烟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨苍天困英雄这般潦倒，\n爱来巴作累囚镇日无聊。\n如鱼纵壑，如鸟归巢。\n在巴黎无非是整顿枪刀。\n那时节才把我恕气全消。\n分出了帝后党扰乱中朝。\n尽心力培植这独立根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜登高坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "滑铁卢已放出人马一标。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃戎装上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来者敢是惠林吞？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "然也！拿破仑，你早早投降，本帅饶你不死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说，看枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃败下，赵瑶颜追下。赵晃扮小生上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小生哥伦布。只因泛舟航海，见前面白茫茫一片，却有二三黑点，又流出许多\n萍藻，必然大陆无疑。所以禀明我国女主，要她给发盘川。等吾去寻找这块殖\n民之地。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山重水复疑无路，柳暗花明又一村。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜雉冠扮女王上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃西班牙女主是也。昨日哥伦布禀请给盘川，要去寻找殖民之地。\n内侍，宣哥伦布上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣哥伦布禀见吾主！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。哥伦布，你此去须要小心才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "拜别了我主上艨艟，\n叹前番只落得劳而无功。\n一霎时又只见天外奇峰。\n兽蹄繁鸟迹广草木蒙茸。\n开关他除非是鬼斧神工。\n一叶舟归国去奏与九重。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃下。赵瑶颜扮女将上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家约翰，乃法兰西人氏。皆因英吉利，把我邦杀得大败全输，几乎国破家亡。\n奴家一时气忿填胸，带领许多人马，忘生舍死，与他一战。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四十万人齐解甲，并无一个是男儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃扮英将上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔约翰，你是个小小的女子，怎敢抗我天兵！少时擒住，将你碎尸万段。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不必多言，放马过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜杀赵晃败下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见英将在阵前打马逃遁，\n回头来又谢过大小三军。\n才不负平日里浩荡皇恩。\n何况是大罗天催返灵魂。\n有一言要诸君洗耳恭听：\n从今后休忘了保扶乾坤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜作跳状，下。赵晃纱帽红袍上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫梅特涅。自从把新党一齐捕捉，陷在监牢，老夫恐怕斩草不除根，逢春又\n发青，因此将他们一个个定成死罪。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨小非君子，无毒不丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃坐。赵瑶颜扮刺客上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，刺客。只为梅特涅伤天害理，俺要去取他的首级，以为众新党报仇雪恨。\n来此已是他的府第了，待我飞身进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜作跳，见赵晃，欲刺。赵晃惊倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "见奸贼不由我心中似火，\n你不该在国中逼设网罗。\n就是那羽翼人零落无多。\n眼睁睁送奸贼去见阎罗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜将赵晃刺死。赵瑶颜、赵晃同下。赵晃扮时挂装短须上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "床头黄金尽，壮士无颜色。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下康有为，祖籍广东南海，东届得中一名乡榜。因此进京会试，路过上海，\n迷恋烟花。看看把盘川用尽，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "万事都由一念差，\n不该如此恋烟花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天吓天吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "公车何日到京华？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜扮妓女上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "歌能常叫善才服，妆成每被秋娘妒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我朱宝仙，是该搭有名气格倌人。新近做着仔个康有为，今日吃酒，明朝碰和，\n看看局账，倒着宝担点心事。听见说俚耐住勒一爿客栈里，让倪去看看苗头。\n阿虎叔！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内应。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "轿子上来，到康老爷住格格爿栈房去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下，赵晃慌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刚才茶房报道：朱宝仙前来找我。倒要躲避开了才好。否则给她看见，不甚方\n便。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦，人呢？啥场花去哉，勿要盘拢勒海，让我闯进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下。赵晃跌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "屋漏更遭连夜雨，\n船危又遇打头风。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，三十六着，走为上着。等她去后，我不免当一票衣服，算清店帐，逃上输\n船去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵晃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劈破玉笼飞彩凤，\n顿开金锁走蛟龙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃下。赵瑶颜上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寻了一泡寻勿着，明朝再来。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "画龙画虎难画骨，知人知面不知心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜下。赵瑶颜时装倌人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门前冷落车马稀，老大嫁作商人妇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家林黛玉。自从跟那天煞的，学会了什么梆子青衣，以为从此可以兴家立业，\n谁知这倒弄得一贫如洗，犹如一梦。今日天煞的出门去了，奴家不如趁空投\n奔月水庵，求悟空师父削发为尼，一则可以忏悔前愆，二则可以修持正果。主\n意已定，就此起身便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想起当年富贵场，\n犹如一梦熟黄粱。\n滴粉搓酥时式妆。\n珠宝还须用斗量。\n忍饥挨饿走四方。\n忏悔除非祷上苍。\n成佛升天尚渺茫。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵瑶颜作进庵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵瑶颜",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将身来至宝殿上，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵晃扮孙悟空出。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "赵晃→赵瑶颜",
          "turns": 43
        },
        {
          "edge": "赵瑶颜→赵晃",
          "turns": 43
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
